aves. It has a sharp venomous stinger on its head.'),(14,'Kakuna','Bug','Poison',45,25,50,25,25,35,_binary '\0','Almost incapable of moving, this POKéMON can only harden its shell to protect itself from predators.'),(15,'Beedrill','Bug','Poison',65,90,40,45,80,75,_binary '\0','It has three poisonous stingers on its forelegs and its tail. They are used to jab its enemy repeatedly.'),(16,'Pidgey','Normal','Flying',40,45,40,35,35,56,_binary '\0','A common sight in forests and woods. It flaps its wings at ground level to kick up blinding sand.'),(17,'Pidgeotto','Normal','Flying',63,60,55,50,50,71,_binary '\0','Very protective of its sprawling territorial area, this POKéMON will fiercely peck at any intruder.'),(18,'Pidgeot','Normal','Flying',83,80,75,70,70,101,_binary '\0','When hunting, it skims the surface of water at high speed to pick off unwary prey such as MAGIKARP.'),(19,'Rattata','Normal','',30,56,35,25,35,72,_binary '\0','Bites anything when it attacks. Small and very quick, it is a common sight in many places.'),(20,'Raticate','Normal','',55,81,60,50,70,97,_binary '\0','It uses its whis­ kers to maintain its balance. It apparently slows down if they are cut off.'),(21,'Spearow','Normal','Flying',40,60,30,31,31,70,_binary '\0','It flaps its small wings busily to fly. Using its beak, it searches in grass for prey.'),(22,'Fearow','Normal','Flying',65,90,65,61,61,100,_binary '\0','With its huge and magnificent wings, it can keep aloft without ever having to land for rest.'),(23,'Ekans','Poison','',35,60,44,40,54,55,_binary '\0','Moves silently and stealthily. Eats the eggs of birds, such as PIDGEY and SPEAROW, whole.'),(24,'Arbok','Poison','',60,85,69,65,79,80,_binary '\0','It is rumored that the ferocious warning markings on its belly differ from area to area.'),(25,'Pikachu','Electric','',35,55,40,50,50,90,_binary '\0','When several of these POKéMON gather, their electricity could build and cause lightning storms.'),(26,'Raichu','Electric','',60,90,55,90,80,110,_binary '\0','Its long tail serves as a ground to protect itself from its own high-voltage power.'),(27,'Sandshrew','Ground','',50,75,85,20,30,40,_binary '\0','Burrows deep underground in arid locations far from water. It only emerges to hunt for food.'),(28,'Sandslash','Ground','',75,100,110,45,55,65,_binary '\0','Curls up into a spiny ball when threatened. It can roll while curled up to attack or escape.'),(29,'Nidoran♀','Poison','',55,47,52,40,40,41,_binary '\0','Although small, its venomous barbs render this POKéMON dangerous. The female has smaller horns.'),(30,'Nidorina','Poison','',70,62,67,55,55,56,_binary '\0','The female\'s horn develops slowly. Prefers physical attacks such as clawing and biting.'),(31,'Nidoqueen','Poison','Ground',90,92,87,75,85,76,_binary '\0','Its hard scales provide strong protection. It uses its hefty bulk to execute powerful moves.'),(32,'Nidoran♂','Poison','',46,57,40,40,40,50,_binary '\0','Stiffens its ears to sense danger. The larger its horns, the more powerful its secreted venom.'),(33,'Nidorino','Poison','',61,72,57,55,55,65,_binary '\0','An aggressive POKéMON that is quick to attack. The horn on its head secretes a powerful venom.'),(34,'Nidoking','Poison','Ground',81,102,77,85,75,85,_binary '\0','It uses its powerful tail in battle to smash, constrict, then break the prey\'s bones.'),(35,'Clefairy','Fairy','',70,45,48,60,65,35,_binary '\0','Its magical and cute appeal has many admirers. It is rare and found only in certain areas.'),(36,'Clefable','Fairy','',95,70,73,95,90,60,_binary '\0','A timid fairy POKéMON that is rarely seen. It will run and hide the moment it senses people.'),(37,'Vulpix','Fire','',38,41,40,50,65,65,_binary '\0','At the time of birth, it has just one tail. The tail splits from its tip as it grows older.'),(38,'Ninetales','Fire','',73,76,75,81,100,100,_binary '\0','Very smart and very vengeful. Grabbing one of its many tails could result in a 1000-year curse.'),(39,'Jigglypuff','Normal','Fairy',115,45,20,45,25,20,_binary '\0','When its huge eyes light up, it sings a mysteriously soothing melody that lulls its enemies to sleep.'),(40,'Wigglytuff','Normal','Fairy',140,70,45,85,50,45,_binary '\0','The body is soft and rubbery. When angered, it will suck in air and inflate itself to an enormous size.'),(41,'Zubat','Poison','Flying',40,45,35,30,40,55,_binary '\0','Forms colonies in perpetually dark places. Uses ultrasonic waves to identify and approach targets.'),(42,'Golbat','Poison','Flying',75,80,70,65,75,90,_binary '\0','Once it strikes, it will not stop draining energy from the victim even if it gets too heavy to fly.'),(43,'Oddish','Grass','Poison',45,50,55,75,65,30,_binary '\0','During the day, it keeps its face buried in the ground. At night, it wanders around sowing its seeds.'),(44,'Gloom','Grass','Poison',60,65,70,85,75,40,_binary '\0','The fluid that oozes from its mouth isn\'t drool. It is a nectar that is used to attract prey.'),(45,'Vileplume','Grass','Poison',75,80,85,110,90,50,_binary '\0','It has the world’s largest petals. With every step, the petals shake out heavy clouds of toxic pollen.'),(46,'Paras','Bug','Grass',35,70,55,45,55,25,_binary '\0','Burrows to suck tree roots. The mushrooms on its back grow by draw­ ing nutrients from the bug host.'),(47,'Parasect','Bug','Grass',60,95,80,60,80,30,_binary '\0','A host-parasite pair in which the parasite mushroom has taken over the host bug. Prefers damp places.'),(48,'Venonat','Bug','Poison',60,55,50,40,55,45,_binary '\0','Lives in the shadows of tall trees where it eats insects. It is attracted by light at night.'),(49,'Venomoth','Bug','Poison',70,65,60,90,75,90,_binary '\0','The dustlike scales covering its wings are color-coded to indicate the kinds of poison it has.'),(50,'Diglett','Ground','',10,55,25,35,45,95,_binary '\0','Lives about one yard underground where it feeds on plant roots. It sometimes appears above ground.'),(51,'Dugtrio','Ground','',35,80,50,50,70,120,_binary '\0','A team of DIGLETT triplets. It triggers huge earthquakes by burrowing 60 miles underground.'),(52,'Meowth','Normal','',40,45,35,40,40,90,_binary '\0','It washes its face regularly to keep the coin on its forehead spotless. It doesn’t get along with Galarian Meowth.'),(53,'Persian','Normal','',65,70,60,65,65,115,_binary '\0','Although its fur has many admirers, it is tough to raise as a pet because of its fickle meanness.'),(54,'Psyduck','Water','',50,52,48,65,50,55,_binary '\0','While lulling its enemies with its vacant look, this wily POKéMON will use psychokinetic powers.'),(55,'Golduck','Water','',80,82,78,95,80,85,_binary '\0','Often seen swim­ ming elegantly by lake shores. It is often mistaken for the Japanese monster, Kappa.'),(56,'Mankey','Fighting','',40,80,35,35,45,70,_binary '\0','Extremely quick to anger. It could be docile one moment then thrashing away the next instant.'),(57,'Primeape','Fighting','',65,105,60,60,70,95,_binary '\0','Always furious and tenacious to boot. It will not abandon chasing its quarry until it is caught.'),(58,'Growlithe','Fire','',55,70,45,70,50,60,_binary '\0','Very protective of its territory. It will bark and bite to repel intruders from its space.'),(59,'Arcanine','Fire','',90,110,80,100,80,95,_binary '\0','A POKéMON that has been admired since the past for its beauty. It runs agilely as if on wings.'),(60,'Poliwag','Water','',40,50,40,40,40,90,_binary '\0','Its newly grown legs prevent it from running. It appears to prefer swimming than trying to stand.'),(61,'Poliwhirl','Water','',65,65,65,50,50,90,_binary '\0','Capable of living in or out of water. When out of water, it sweats to keep its body slimy.'),(62,'Poliwrath','Water','Fighting',90,95,95,70,90,70,_binary '\0','An adept swimmer at both the front crawl and breast stroke. Easily overtakes the best human swimmers.'),(63,'Abra','Psychic','',25,20,15,105,55,90,_binary '\0','Using its ability to read minds, it will identify impending danger and TELEPORT to safety.'),(64,'Kadabra','Psychic','',40,35,30,120,70,105,_binary '\0','It emits special alpha waves from its body that induce headaches just by being close by.'),(65,'Alakazam','Psychic','',55,50,45,135,95,120,_binary '\0','Its brain can out­ perform a super­ computer. Its intelligence quotient is said to be 5,000.'),(66,'Machop','Fighting','',70,80,50,35,35,35,_binary '\0','Loves to build its muscles. It trains in all styles of martial arts to become even stronger.'),(67,'Machoke','Fighting','',80,100,70,50,60,45,_binary '\0','Its muscular body is so powerful, it must wear a power save belt to be able to regulate its motions.'),(68,'Machamp','Fighting','',90,130,80,65,85,55,_binary '\0','Using its heavy muscles, it throws powerful punches that can send the victim clear over the horizon.'),(69,'Bellsprout','Grass','Poison',50,75,35,70,30,40,_binary '\0','A carnivorous POKéMON that traps and eats bugs. It uses its root feet to soak up needed moisture.'),(70,'Weepinbell','Grass','Poison',65,90,50,85,45,55,_binary '\0','It spits out POISONPOWDER to immobilize the enemy and then finishes it with a spray of ACID.'),(71,'Victreebel','Grass','Poison',80,105,65,100,70,70,_binary '\0','Said to live in huge colonies deep in jungles, although no one has ever returned from there.'),(72,'Tentacool','Water','Poison',40,40,35,50,100,70,_binary '\0','Drifts in shallow seas. Anglers who hook them by accident are often punished by its stinging acid.'),(73,'Tentacruel','Water','Poison',80,70,65,80,120,100,_binary '\0','The tentacles are normally kept short. On hunts, they are extended to ensnare and immobilize prey.'),(74,'Geodude','Rock','Ground',40,80,100,30,30,20,_binary '\0','Found in fields and mountains. Mistaking them for boulders, people often step or trip on them.'),(75,'Graveler','Rock','Ground',55,95,115,45,45,35,_binary '\0','Rolls down slopes to move. It rolls over any obstacle without slowing or changing its direction.'),(76,'Golem','Rock','Ground',80,120,130,55,65,45,_binary '\0','Its boulder-like body is extremely hard. It can easily withstand dynamite blasts without damage.'),(77,'Ponyta','Fire','',50,85,55,65,65,90,_binary '\0','Its hooves are 10 times harder than diamonds. It can trample anything completely flat in little time.'),(78,'Rapidash','Fire','',65,100,70,80,80,105,_binary '\0','Very competitive, this POKéMON will chase anything that moves fast in the hopes of racing it.'),(79,'Slowpoke','Water','Psychic',90,65,65,40,40,15,_binary '\0','Incredibly slow and dopey. It takes 5 seconds for it to feel pain when under attack.'),(80,'Slowbro','Water','Psychic',95,75,110,100,80,30,_binary '\0','The SHELLDER that is latched onto SLOWPOKE\'s tail is said to feed on the host\'s left over scraps.'),(81,'Magnemite','Electric','Steel',25,35,70,95,55,45,_binary '\0','Uses anti-gravity to stay suspended. Appears without warning and uses THUNDER WAVE and similar moves.'),(82,'Magneton','Electric','Steel',50,60,95,120,70,70,_binary '\0','Formed by several MAGNEMITEs linked together. They frequently appear when sunspots flare up.'),(83,'Farfetch\'d','Normal','Flying',52,65,55,58,62,60,_binary '\0','The sprig of green onions it holds is its weapon. It is used much like a metal sword.'),(84,'Doduo','Normal','Flying',35,85,45,35,35,75,_binary '\0','A bird that makes up for its poor flying with its fast foot speed. Leaves giant footprints.'),(85,'Dodrio','Normal','Flying',60,110,70,60,60,100,_binary '\0','Uses its three brains to execute complex plans. While two heads sleep, one head stays awake.'),(86,'Seel','Water','',65,45,55,45,70,45,_binary '\0','The protruding horn on its head is very hard. It is used for bashing through thick ice.'),(87,'Dewgong','Water','Ice',90,70,80,70,95,70,_binary '\0','Stores thermal energy in its body. Swims at a steady 8 knots even in intensely cold waters.'),(88,'Grimer','Poison','',80,80,50,40,50,25,_binary '\0','Appears in filthy areas. Thrives by sucking up polluted sludge that is pumped out of factories.'),(89,'Muk','Poison','',105,105,75,65,100,50,_binary '\0','Thickly covered with a filthy, vile sludge. It is so toxic, even its footprints contain poison.'),(90,'Shellder','Water','',30,65,100,45,25,40,_binary '\0','Its hard shell repels any kind of attack. It is vulnerable only when its shell is open.'),(91,'Cloyster','Water','Ice',50,95,180,85,45,70,_binary '\0','When attacked, it launches its horns in quick volleys. Its innards have never been seen.'),(92,'Gastly','Ghost','Poison',30,35,30,100,35,80,_binary '\0','Almost invisible, this gaseous POKéMON cloaks the target and puts it to sleep without notice.'),(93,'Haunter','Ghost','Poison',45,50,45,115,55,95,_binary '\0','Because of its ability to slip through block walls, it is said to be from an­ other dimension.'),(94,'Gengar','Ghost','Poison',60,65,60,130,75,110,_binary '\0','Under a full moon, this POKéMON likes to mimic the shadows of people and laugh at their fright.'),(95,'Onix','Rock','Ground',35,45,160,30,45,70,_binary '\0','As it grows, the stone portions of its body harden to become similar to a diamond, but colored black.'),(96,'Drowzee','Psychic','',60,48,45,43,90,42,_binary '\0','Puts enemies to sleep then eats their dreams. Occasionally gets sick from eating bad dreams.'),(97,'Hypno','Psychic','',85,73,70,73,115,67,_binary '\0','When it locks eyes with an enemy, it will use a mix of PSI moves such as HYPNOSIS and CONFUSION.'),(98,'Krabby','Water','',30,105,90,25,25,50,_binary '\0','Its pincers are not only powerful weapons, they are used for balance when walking sideways.'),(99,'Kingler','Water','',55,130,115,50,50,75,_binary '\0','The large pincer has 10000 hp of crushing power. However, its huge size makes it unwieldy to use.'),(100,'Voltorb','Electric','',40,30,50,55,55,100,_binary '\0','Usually found in power plants. Easily mistaken for a POKé BALL, they have zapped many people.'),(101,'Electrode','Electric','',60,50,70,80,80,140,_binary '\0','It stores electric energy under very high pressure. It often explodes with little or no provocation.'),(102,'Exeggcute','Grass','Psychic',60,40,80,60,45,40,_binary '\0','Often mistaken for eggs. When disturbed, they quickly gather and attack in swarms.'),(103,'Exeggutor','Grass','Psychic',95,95,85,125,65,55,_binary '\0','Legend has it that on rare occasions, one of its heads will drop off and continue on as an EXEGGCUTE.'),(104,'Cubone','Ground','',50,50,95,40,50,35,_binary '\0','Because it never removes its skull helmet, no one has ever seen this POKéMON\'s real face.'),(105,'Marowak','Ground','',60,80,110,50,80,45,_binary '\0','The bone it holds is its key weapon. It throws the bone skillfully like a boomerang to KO targets.'),(106,'Hitmonlee','Fighting','',50,120,53,35,110,87,_binary '\0','When in a hurry, its legs lengthen progressively. It runs smoothly with extra long, loping strides.'),(107,'Hitmonchan','Fighting','',50,105,79,35,110,76,_binary '\0','While apparently doing nothing, it fires punches in lightning fast volleys that are impossible to see.'),(108,'Lickitung','Normal','',90,55,75,60,75,30,_binary '\0','Its tongue can be extended like a chameleon\'s. It leaves a tingling sensation when it licks enemies.'),(109,'Koffing','Poison','',40,65,95,60,45,35,_binary '\0','Because it stores several kinds of toxic gases in its body, it is prone to exploding without warning.'),(110,'Weezing','Poison','',65,90,120,85,70,60,_binary '\0','Where two kinds of poison gases meet, 2 KOFFINGs can fuse into a WEEZING over many years.'),(111,'Rhyhorn','Ground','Rock',80,85,95,30,30,25,_binary '\0','A POKéMON with a one-track mind. Once it charges, it won\'t stop running until it falls asleep.'),(112,'Rhydon','Ground','Rock',105,130,120,45,45,40,_binary '\0','Protected by an armor-like hide, it is capable of living in molten lava of 3,600 degrees.'),(113,'Chansey','Normal','',250,5,5,35,105,50,_binary '\0','A rare and elusive POKéMON that is said to bring happiness to those who manage to get it.'),(114,'Tangela','Grass','',65,55,115,100,40,60,_binary '\0','The whole body is swathed with wide vines that are similar to sea­ weed. Its vines shake as it walks.'),(115,'Kangaskhan','Normal','',105,95,80,40,80,90,_binary '\0','The infant rarely ventures out of its mother\'s protective pouch until it is 3 years old.'),(116,'Horsea','Water','',30,40,70,70,25,60,_binary '\0','Known to shoot down flying bugs with precision blasts of ink from the surface of the water.'),(117,'Seadra','Water','',55,65,95,95,45,85,_binary '\0','Capable of swim­ ming backwards by rapidly flapping its wing-like pectoral fins and stout tail.'),(118,'Goldeen','Water','',45,67,60,35,50,63,_binary '\0','Its tail fin billows like an elegant ballroom dress, giving it the nickname of the Water Queen.'),(119,'Seaking','Water','',80,92,65,65,80,68,_binary '\0','In the autumn spawning season, they can be seen swimming powerfully up rivers and creeks.'),(120,'Staryu','Water','',30,45,55,70,55,85,_binary '\0','If its body is torn, it can grow back if the red core remains. The core flashes at midnight.'),(121,'Starmie','Water','Psychic',60,75,85,100,85,115,_binary '\0','Its central core glows with the seven colors of the rainbow. Some people value the core as a gem.'),(122,'Mr. Mime','Psychic','Fairy',40,45,65,100,120,90,_binary '\0','If interrupted while it is miming, it will slap around the offender with its broad hands.'),(123,'Scyther','Bug','Flying',70,110,80,55,80,105,_binary '\0','With ninja-like agility and speed, it can create the illusion that there is more than one.'),(124,'Jynx','Ice','Psychic',65,50,35,115,95,95,_binary '\0','It seductively wiggles its hips as it walks. It can cause people to dance in unison with it.'),(125,'Electabuzz','Electric','',65,83,57,95,85,105,_binary '\0','Normally found near power plants, they can wander away and cause major blackouts in cities.'),(126,'Magmar','Fire','',65,95,57,100,85,93,_binary '\0','Its body always burns with an orange glow that enables it to hide perfectly among flames.'),(127,'Pinsir','Bug','',65,125,100,55,70,85,_binary '\0','If it fails to crush the victim in its pincers, it will swing it around and toss it hard.'),(128,'Tauros','Normal','',75,100,95,40,70,110,_binary '\0','When it targets an enemy, it charges furiously while whipping its body with its long tails.'),(129,'Magikarp','Water','',20,10,55,15,20,80,_binary '\0','In the distant past, it was somewhat stronger than the horribly weak descendants that exist today.'),(130,'Gyarados','Water','Flying',95,125,79,60,100,81,_binary '\0','Once it begins to rampage, a GYARADOS will burn everything down, even in a harsh storm.'),(131,'Lapras','Water','Ice',130,85,80,85,95,60,_binary '\0','A POKéMON that has been over­ hunted almost to extinction. It can ferry people across the water.'),(132,'Ditto','Normal','',48,48,48,48,48,48,_binary '\0','Capable of copying an enemy\'s genetic code to instantly transform itself into a duplicate of the enemy.'),(133,'Eevee','Normal','',55,55,50,45,65,55,_binary '\0','Its genetic code is irregular. It may mutate if it is exposed to radiation from element STONEs.'),(134,'Vaporeon','Water','',130,65,60,110,95,65,_binary '\0','Lives close to water. Its long tail is ridged with a fin which is often mistaken for a mermaid\'s.'),(135,'Jolteon','Electric','',65,65,60,110,95,130,_binary '\0','It accumulates negative ions in the atmosphere to blast out 10000- volt lightning bolts.'),(136,'Flareon','Fire','',65,130,60,95,110,65,_binary '\0','When storing thermal energy in its body, its temperature could soar to over 1600 degrees.'),(137,'Porygon','Normal','',65,60,70,85,75,40,_binary '\0','A POKéMON that consists entirely of programming code. Capable of moving freely in cyberspace.'),(138,'Omanyte','Rock','Water',35,40,100,90,55,35,_binary '\0','Although long extinct, in rare cases, it can be genetically resurrected from fossils.'),(139,'Omastar','Rock','Water',70,60,125,115,70,55,_binary '\0','A prehistoric POKéMON that died out when its heavy shell made it impossible to catch prey.'),(140,'Kabuto','Rock','Water',30,80,90,55,45,55,_binary '\0','A POKéMON that was resurrected from a fossil found in what was once the ocean floor eons ago.'),(141,'Kabutops','Rock','Water',60,115,105,65,70,80,_binary '\0','Its sleek shape is perfect for swim­ ming. It slashes prey with its claws and drains the body fluids.'),(142,'Aerodactyl','Rock','Flying',80,105,65,60,75,130,_binary '\0','A Pokémon that roamed the skies in the dinosaur era. Its teeth are like saw blades.'),(143,'Snorlax','Normal','',160,110,65,65,110,30,_binary '\0','Very lazy. Just eats and sleeps. As its rotund bulk builds, it becomes steadily more slothful.'),(144,'Articuno','Ice','Flying',90,85,100,95,125,85,_binary '','A legendary bird POKéMON that is said to appear to doomed people who are lost in icy mountains.'),(145,'Zapdos','Electric','Flying',90,90,85,125,90,100,_binary '','A legendary bird POKéMON that is said to appear from clouds while dropping enormous lightning bolts.'),(146,'Moltres','Fire','Flying',90,100,90,125,85,90,_binary '','Known as the legendary bird of fire. Every flap of its wings creates a dazzling flash of flames.'),(147,'Dratini','Dragon','',41,64,45,50,50,50,_binary '\0','Long considered a mythical POKéMON until recently when a small colony was found living underwater.'),(148,'Dragonair','Dragon','',61,84,65,70,70,70,_binary '\0','A mystical POKéMON that exudes a gentle aura. Has the ability to change climate conditions.'),(149,'Dragonite','Dragon','Flying',91,134,95,100,100,80,_binary '\0','An extremely rarely seen marine POKéMON. Its intelligence is said to match that of humans.'),(150,'Mewtwo','Psychic','',106,110,90,154,90,130,_binary '','It was created by a scientist after years of horrific gene splicing and DNA engineering experiments.'),(151,'Mew','Psychic','',100,100,100,100,100,100,_binary '\0','So rare that it is still said to be a mirage by many experts. Only a few people have seen it worldwide.'),(152,'Chikorita','Grass','',45,49,65,49,65,45,_bi