grees F.'),(379,'Registeel','Steel','',80,75,150,75,150,50,_binary '','REGISTEEL has a body that is harder than any kind of metal. Its body is apparently hollow. No one has any idea what this POKéMON eats.'),(380,'Latias','Dragon','Psychic',80,80,90,110,130,110,_binary '','LATIAS is highly sensitive to the emotions of people. If it senses any hostility, this POKéMON ruffles the feathers all over its body and cries shrilly to intimidate the foe.'),(381,'Latios','Dragon','Psychic',80,90,80,130,110,110,_binary '','LATIOS has the ability to make its foe see an image of what it has seen or imagines in its head. This POKéMON is intelligent and understands human speech.'),(382,'Kyogre','Water','',100,100,90,150,140,90,_binary '','KYOGRE has the power to create massive rain clouds that cover the entire sky and bring about torrential downpours. This POKéMON saved people who were suffering from droughts.'),(383,'Groudon','Ground','',100,150,140,100,90,90,_binary '','GROUDON has long been described in mythology as the POKéMON that raised lands and expanded continents. This POKéMON took to sleep after a cataclysmic battle with KYOGRE.'),(384,'Rayquaza','Dragon','Flying',105,150,90,150,90,95,_binary '','RAYQUAZA lived for hundreds of millions of years in the earth’s ozone layer, never descending to the ground. This POKéMON appears to feed on water and particles in the atmosphere.'),(385,'Jirachi','Steel','Psychic',100,100,100,100,100,100,_binary '','A legend states that JIRACHI will make true any wish that is written on notes attached to its head when it awakens. If this POKéMON senses danger, it will fight without awakening.'),(386,'Deoxys','Psychic','',50,150,50,150,50,150,_binary '','The DNA of a space virus underwent a sudden mutation upon exposure to a laser beam and resulted in DEOXYS. The crystalline organ on this POKéMON’s chest appears to be its brain.'),(387,'Turtwig','Grass','',55,68,64,45,55,31,_binary '\0','Made from soil, the shell on its back hardens when 